cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.NE 

The paper discusses a deep learning model for classification problems, specifically using deep forest ensemble. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the model is applied to image classification tasks, which suggests the sub-category cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the second likely option. The paper also discusses the use of boosting algorithms and hyper-parameter optimization, which are common topics in the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the use of deep learning models and ensembles suggests the sub-category cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as a possible option.
